    .major
      Curriculum
    .quote
      RubyonRailsTutor consists of 10 sequenced lessons designed to teach the building blocks of Rails MVC based Web Software.  
    .quote 
      The sequence of lessons is organized around a Cohort of students, each cohort contains 5 students.
    .quote 
      Learning sessions utilize virtual pair programming, all content, learning and interaction is delivered through the internet using tools like floobits and google hangouts.  
    .quote 
      All lessons are taught by John Davison, a bay area expert on teaching Ruby on Rails to beginners. 
    .quote 
      The next cohort starts on Monday October 21, lessons take place every Monday and Wednesday night from 7-9pm PST and run for 5 weeks.  
